Reference: `docs/RELEASE_CHECKLIST.md`, `docs/exec-plans/v0.2-private-beta.md`.

## Automated gate

- Clean git status for intended release files.
- `npm run validate:env` (when env available).
- `npm run typecheck`, `npm run lint`, `npm test`.
- `npm run api:worker:test`; `npm run api:worker:verify` when Worker URL configured.
- `npm run audit:frontend-secrets`, `npm run audit:deps`.
- `npm run build` with real production env (HTTPS `VITE_API_BASE_URL`, no mock AI).
- `npm run android:build:verify` for APK.

## Manual gate

- OTP auth on production Supabase configuration.
- Full authenticated Basic debate with evaluation and quota behaviour.
- Network/provider failure recovery; close/reopen persistence.
- Feedback submission path.
- Physical Android: Back, safe areas, logout/restart, German/long-text layouts.

## Blockers

- Placeholder API URLs in production builds.
- Uncommitted secrets, `.env` files, or generated `dist/` / APK artifacts in release commits.
- Undocumented known limitations.
